name: Apple AirPods Max - Silver
description: This item is a high-performance headphone that offers an immersive audio experience with its dynamic driver, active noise cancellation, and spatial audio with dynamic head tracking. It also features transparency mode to stay aware of the surroundings. The headphone is designed with a knit-mesh canopy and memory foam ear cushions for comfort, while the computational audio technology with Apple H1 chip offers an exceptional listening experience.
